CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781581669
OL,3,CEngland fans embracing Texas culture
OL,4,Cas Three Lions prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FThe group said they had travelled
OL,8,Fthousands of miles to follow England,
OL,9,Fwith Mitch revealing he would briefly
OL,10,Freturn to the UK before flying back to
OL,11,Fthe United States.
OL,13,F"We're flying back ` we've got three
OL,14,Fdays in Stoke and then back to
OL,15,FBoston," he said.
OL,17,FAsked why he was making the whirlwind
OL,18,Freturn trip, Mitch added: "Just to see
OL,19,Fthe kids, and for Father's Day."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@HO]zD@[OU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
