OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781581669
OL,3,CEngland fans embracing Texas culture
OL,4,Cas Three Lions prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FHis friend Simon said: "We've just got
OL,8,Fto do that little bit haven't we."
OL,10,FMitch said the locals had made the
OL,11,Ftrip particularly memorable.
OL,13,F"The Americans have been sound, we
OL,14,Fwere drinking with them last night and
OL,15,Fthey're coming out with us today `
OL,16,Fbrilliant," he said.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@bO]uD@AOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
