OL,3,CEngland fans embracing Texas culture
OL,4,Cas Three Lions prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FElsewhere in Fort Worth, another group
OL,8,Fof supporters said they had been
OL,9,Fpriced out of following England deeper
OL,10,Finto the tournament despite regularly
OL,11,Fattending major competitions.
OL,13,FOne fan, who gave his name as Chris,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We would usually do multiple
OL,15,Fgames over a World Cup or a Euros but
OL,16,Fwe're only doing one game."
OL,18,FHis friend Matt added: "We could have
OL,19,Fall got a ticket to the final, but it
OL,20,Fwas like five-and-a-half grand for a
OL,21,Fticket so we've had to say no.
OL,26,@vD@GOUxD@[O]zD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781581669
OL,3,CEngland fans embracing Texas culture
OL,4,Cas Three Lions prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,F"If we get to the final it's going to
OL,8,Fbe a tough pill to swallow because
OL,9,Fwe're not going to be there.
OL,11,F"It's the first time in eight
OL,12,Ftournaments we've not pre-ordered a
OL,13,Ffinal ticket," he said."
OL,15,FFellow England fan Rowan said Fort
OL,16,FWorth had proved an ideal place to
OL,17,Fexperience the tournament atmosphere.
OL,19,F"We're in Fort Worth, it's a great
OL,20,Fexperience, it's unbelievable," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUuD@NO]uD@XO]{D@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
