OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781581669
OL,3,CEngland fans embracing Texas culture
OL,4,Cas Three Lions prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,F"We're all in cowboy hats ` they're
OL,8,Fnot doing that in Los Angeles or
OL,9,FBoston."
OL,11,FDan Stapleton, 28, travelled to Texas
OL,12,Fwith his father Mark as part of a
OL,13,Fwider American road trip which
OL,14,Fincluded football and sightseeing.
OL,16,F"It's one way to spend Father's Day,"
OL,17,FDan said.
OL,19,FMark, 62, said: "Well that's just part
OL,20,Fof it, it's actually a much longer
OL,21,Ftrip.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@HO]xD@AOUxD@eO]{D@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781581669
OL,3,CEngland fans embracing Texas culture
OL,4,Cas Three Lions prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,F"We've already been to see the Dutch
OL,8,Fvs Japan game and then we're obviously
OL,9,Fhere for England vs Croatia.
OL,11,F"But then it's part of a road trip `
OL,12,Fso we're going to go to Nashville and
OL,13,FNew Orleans for a music break and then
OL,14,Fover to Philly and Boston."
OL,16,FDan said he had always wanted to visit
OL,17,FTexas and had been fortunate to secure
OL,18,Ftickets before the draw was made.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@[O]
