OL,3,CEngland fans embracing Texas culture
OL,4,Cas Three Lions prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,FAsked who planned the trip, Mark
OL,8,Fjoked: "I wouldn't have had any
OL,9,Ftickets really without my son being
OL,10,Flucky in the draw ` and then I was
OL,11,Ffunding most of it."
OL,13,FThe pair also questioned the
OL,14,Faffordability of attending matches.
OL,16,FDan said: "I'm not sure this is a
OL,17,Ftournament for the youngsters ` or
OL,18,FEngland fans or football fans in
OL,19,Fgeneral to be honest.
OL,26,@pD@HOUsD@TO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
