OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781581669
OL,3,CEngland fans embracing Texas culture
OL,4,Cas Three Lions prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Copener
OL,7,F"There will be people who will be
OL,8,Funhappy with that."
OL,10,FMark added: "I have a friend who said
OL,11,Fhe just bought some quarter-final
OL,12,Ftickets for just over #2,000 ` so it
OL,13,Fis a bit expensive, let's be honest."
OL,15,FInstead, they had chosen to spend time
OL,16,Fexploring Texas itself.
OL,18,F"We came up to Fort Worth to see
OL,19,Fproper Texas," Mark said.
